message: To get 100 value: combine one magical liquid with one mundane liquid, then use the 'filter' tool. Alternatively, combine one magical solid with one mundane solid, then use the 'vial' tool. Avoid combining two items of the same 'type' (e.g., two magical solids, or two mundane solids), as this often results in negative or lower values.
